By BO Staff Writer The following is an invite by the Black First Land First movement to their Black Business seminar. It is with great pleasure, on behalf of the Black First Land First National Convener, Andile Mngxitama, to invite you to the BLF inaugural Black Business Seminar on 03 December 2016 at Southern Sun Pretoria at 18h00. The seminar seeks to assist Africans to tackle challenges that affect the growth and sustainability of  black owned businesses, while pushing the black agenda for change in South Africa’s predominantly white controlled economy. Please feel free to contact Manku Baloyi on 078 291 9553, should you have any queries.